[Verse 1: Crucial Star]
Nae gieok soge areungeorineun neoui
Eolgureun areumdapge seulpeo boyeosseo
Chagaun nareul nogiryeo haessdeon neoui
Nungaen ttatteushan nunmuri goyeosseo
Gyejeoreun byeonhago
Angsanghaessdeon nae maeumen
Dasi kkocci pieonago
Hwansangeul pumgoseo
Jeo meolli yeohaengeul tteonassdeon
Nan dasi yeoneocheoreom neoegero

