Biga ssodajineun bam
Machi dejabyucheoreom
Jip ape meomchun sungan
Tteooreun geunarui daehwa
Geuttae nan nunmureul boimyeo
Neoege jalmoseul bireossgo
Du beon dasin bogi silhdahan neon
Milchyeonaessji nal
Eonjedeun dasi neol
Gajil su isseulgeora saenggakhaessji
Naega wonhal ttaemyeon
But geugeon naega mandeureonaen gwebyeon
Nae jasineul bangeohagi wihae
Jojakhaenwassdeon gieok
Jeomjeom seonmyeonghaejigo nan muneojyeo

